fields.title: Trng chin thm ngon n gin
fields.description:
Trng chin l mt mn n quen thuc trong ba cm hng ngy ca ngi Vit, c yu thch bi cch lm n gin, nguyn liu d tm v hng v thm ngon, hp dn. Mc d l mn n c bn, nhng ch cn mt cht bin tu v kho lo, bn hon ton c th to ra mt mn trng chin mm xp, m  v a cm hn bao gi ht.
Trong cng thc ny, mnh s chia s cch lm trng chin n gin nhng y  hng v. Mn n s dng nguyn liu ph bin nh trng g, hnh l, nc mm v mt cht gia v. Bn c th ty chn thm hnh tm phi, tht bm, hoc ph mai  to thm im nhn v  bo cho mn n.
Trng chin ngon nht khi c nh u tay, chin trn la va v dng cho khng dnh  trng khng b kh hay chy. c bit, vic cho thm mt t nc hoc sa ti khi nh trng s gip trng mm hn rt nhiu. Mn trng ny rt thch hp cho ba sng, n cng cm trng nng hi hoc kp vi bnh m cng rt tuyt vi.
Nu bn ang tm kim mt mn n n gin, nhanh gn nhng vn hp dn v y  dinh dng, trng chin l mt la chn hon ho. Hy cng vo bp v th ngay cng thc ny nh!
p trng vo bt, thm nc mm v mui ri nh u.
Cho hnh l xt nh vo hn hp trng, trn u.
Lm nng du n trong cho,  hn hp trng vo.
Chin la va n khi trng vng u hai mt th gp ra a.
